<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7365219">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7365219/" class="title-link">评《哲学是什么》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7365219"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/michealtwisse/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1711168-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/michealtwisse/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Barton</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-02-02"
      class="main-meta">2015-02-02 12:35:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7365219_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很好的哲学启蒙书，通过本书能够对哲学主要研究哪些方向有一个总体的把握，然后再挑自己有兴趣的方向去读和学习，看完全书，我觉得“伦理学”，政治哲学，宗教哲学，这几章最有意思，最能与现实有联系。 伦理学中关于道德的讨论，关于康德的绝对命令，都是那么引人思考。 政治...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7365219_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7365219_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










